This is a readaptation of the Pascal syntax definition ("pas.lang") that ships
with Highlight; it was tweaked to cover Delphi native types and keywords.

It doesn't cover fully the Delphi syntax -- I've just updated the list of native
data types keywords, as a way of "patching holes", but no effort was taken to
systematically go over the full syntax definition to make it fully compliant
to Delphi.

--]]
